<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨ - <span class="c2">(٢٨٣٥)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3889">أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5820">وَأَبُو كُرَيْبٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5577">أَبُو مُعَاوِيَةَ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> إِلَى قَوْلِهِ:</span> كَرَشْحِ الْمِسْكِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>